data.description: This Beautiful home in the sought after neighborhood of Hearthstone lakes is a 3 bedroom 2.5 bath large open concept, with vaulted ceilings in the main living room. Tons of upgrades throughout including Quartz countertops in the Kitchen, LVP flooring, upgrades cabinets, stainless steel appliances and much more! Centrally located to Beaufort, Bluffton and Savannah as well as the military bases. Community features a pool, fitness center, pavilion and playground.
